{"tid":1030814,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利記踢歐聯　文尼家遭爆竊","createTime":"2019-02-21T08:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T13:35:55.000Z","uid":199590,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9001ba06f7266cf481bcc0b5d2d5fcd6c7238b1","tid":1030814,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T08:15:13.000Z","msg":"英國《天空體育》報道，利物浦周二晚在歐聯16強首回合主場鬥拜仁慕尼黑之際，前鋒沙迪奧文尼的居所遭到歹徒爆竊，損失一批財物。<br />\n<br />\n根據報道，當爆竊案發生時，文尼的家中並無任何人，歹徒相信在其家中掠走了手錶、手提電話和車匙等財物；警方亦已經派鑑證科探員在文尼的住所搜證。文尼的住所是在利物浦市的郊區Allerton，這地方位於利物浦市中心東南面約五公里。<br />\n<br />\n沙迪奧文尼的住所在2017年11月亦曾經遭到爆竊，當時這位塞內加爾國腳亦正為紅軍出戰歐聯，在晏菲路鬥馬里博爾。"},{"pid":"e520a68280add422cf3a1f7f3191f121255c46a6","tid":1030814,"uid":16777,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:47:01.000Z","msg":"以為改新聞 隔離奇雲保定又係歐聯期間被人爆格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d0e7a0045305b8dab3461d66af50af286d9556","tid":1030814,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2111c22c76346638c23c23052e15a262acd24543","tid":1030814,"uid":207402,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"會唔會又怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5180601239b9ccb08e3d9b13100bd46c29a62a","tid":1030814,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:35:55.000Z","msg":"英國果邊D球星成日俾人爆竊"}]}